Task 1: Data Validation and Analysis
Objectives
Perform comprehensive column-wise analysis
Clean and preprocess data
Identify critical columns
Generate tags from text fields
Provide actionable insights
Detailed Requirements
1. Column-Wise Analysis
Analyze each column for:
Data type validation
Unique value assessment
Distribution patterns
Stakeholder relevance
Statistical significance
2. Data Cleaning
Handle missing values through:
Appropriate imputation methods
Strategic deletion where necessary
Documentation of cleaning decisions
Address categorical inconsistencies:
Fix typos
Standardize capitalization
Harmonize naming conventions
Process numerical columns:
Format standardization
Outlier detection and handling
Range validation
3. Critical Column Identification
Select and justify top 5 critical columns
Create minimum 3 visualizations:
Bar plots
Distribution charts
Correlation matrices
Document selection rationale
4. Tag Generation
Extract meaningful tags from free text fields:
Failure conditions
Component information
Common patterns
Create standardized tagging system
5. Synthesis and Key Takeaways
Document data discrepancies
Summarize generated tags
Provide actionable recommendations
List additional insights
Deliverables
Cleaned dataset (CSV/Excel)
2-page detailed report
Python analysis scripts
